## Information Sharing Resource Hub
This guidance is a good option for anyone who needs to share information regularly, especially personal information.
The Government Chief Privacy Officer established the Resource Hub to provide practical advice and tools that help you:
- Ask the right questions so you can set up information sharing arrangements that are safe, effective, legal and ethical;
- Understand what type of sharing may best suit your purpose;
- Avoid having to write everything from scratch;
- Be confident you are meeting best practice as well as complying with the law.
New materials will be added to the hub. Check it out here .
